<h2 class="title"> <a href="/node/1132">Spirit Week</a>
</h2> <span property="dc:title" content="Spirit Week" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><div class="content clearfix"><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded">
<p>Lordstown High School will be having a "Spirit Week" beginning Sunday, March 29.  Various teachers will be posting the spirit week assignments to their google classrooms for students to submit pictures.  </p>
<p>Sunday, March 29: Family Fun Night- watch a movie, build a puzzle, play a board game - submit a photo having fun with your family</p>
<p>Monday, March 30: Crazy Hair - whether you wake up with bed hair or style your hair in a wacky way - submit a photo of your crazy hair day</p>
<p>Tuesday, March 31: Great Outdoors- go outside and ride your bike, jump on your trampoline - submit a photo having a great time outside</p>
<p>Wednesday, April 1: Helping Out - sweep the floors, fold some laundry- submit a photo helping out around the house with chores</p>
<p>Thursday, April 2: Pet &amp; Sibling- take a selfie with your pets or siblings - submit a photo hanging out with your pets or siblings</p>
<p>Friday, April 3:  Lordstown Spirit Day- wear your Lordstown gear to show Lordstown Spirit- submit a photo showing school spirit!!</p>
</div></div></div></div>
</div>
